title: There would be no ads.
pid: c3d169c0-5c62-4dfa-aad3-a75be4798c7f
body: |2-
  As a free, open-source, distributed sharing solution, nobody would own Hode, and no single member would be responsible for search results. No member would therefore benefit from injecting ads or otherwise [[id:aa65d20e-1cdd-4b42-8a24-08b2baf59e58][enshittifying]] search results.
